despite that it has nearly twice the Other Odds and Ends Much to my amazement there is no SHO mailing list Maybe because the SHO Registry publication has filled this I haven't joined yet but I've noticed that queries about SHOs still appear on about once a Owners of SHOs are always quick to respond and are very vocal fans of the Maybe some of the most vocal on I've put together the responses to my questions about the cars as well as other posts with useful information on these I'll be posting this in the form of a FAQ If anyone is interested in starting a mailing list please speak up I don't know if I have the resources here at Purdue to start one but maybe someone out there Gene Kim